node.text:
In response to my comic Sun Eater and my recent collaboration with Beyond Kuiper, Audible challenged me to think up my superhero alter ego. I rambled like a mad man at them for a good time before returning to my woodland shack. 

Watch the full video and you be the judge of that. The sick artwork you see from @tenhun is now hanging and framed in my house. Thanks brotha! @audible @heavymetal @matthewmedney
